190
00:23:02,799 --> 00:23:05,119
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, kakav imate stav?

191
00:23:06,480 --> 00:23:11,039
[SPEAKER_00] Pretpostavljam da imate rastući stav i što radite u vezi s tim?

192
00:23:11,759 --> 00:23:12,720
[SPEAKER_00] Kako to radite?

193
00:23:13,519 --> 00:23:14,240
[SPEAKER_00] Kako rastete?

194
00:23:15,839 --> 00:23:16,559
[SPEAKER_00] Kako učite?

195
00:23:17,039 --> 00:23:17,759
[SPEAKER_01] Gdje učite?

196
00:23:18,880 --> 00:23:21,359
